      "text": "# STM32F103 Datasheet Notes\n\nThis local note stands in for imported datasheet excerpts during tests.\n\n- STM32F103 uses an ARM Cortex-M3 core.\n- Flash memory starts at 0x08000000.\n- SRAM starts at 0x20000000.\n- GPIO port C pin 13 is commonly connected to a board LED on small development boards.\n"
